      16  A1    ---     Fcirc     [0/1] Circ flag (2)
  18- 26  F9.4  ---     ecc1s     ?=-999 1sigma upper limit on ecc
  28- 36  F9.4  ---     ecc2s     ?=-999 2sigma upper limit on ecc
